text: Felicity Ann Kendal CBE (born 25 September 1946) is a British actress. She was born in Olton, Warwickshire. She is best known for her role in sitcom The Good Life. She was a contestant in the 2010 series of Strictly Come Dancing. ==Awards== *1976 – Most Promising Newcomer - Variety Club *1979 – Best Actress - Variety Club *1980 – Clarence Derwent Award *1981 - Rear of the Year *1984 – Woman of the Year - Best Actress - Variety Club *1989 – Best Actress - Evening Standard Theatre Awards ==Publication== *White Cargo (memoirs) - 1998 ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English stage actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:People from Warwickshire Category:Strictly Come Dancing participants
